e beyond such definitions by analyzing pictures of family life, weddings, and other "idian scenes of life during the war. Phu thus expands our understanding of how war is waged, experienced, and resolved.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mrz 2022) 0aDocumentary photographyzVietnam. 0aVietnam War, 1961-1975xPhotography. 0aVietnamese diaspora. 0aVietnamesexAttitudes. 0aWar photographyzVietnam. 7aPhotography / Criticism.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDuke University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311074331940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781478012917zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781478012917423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781478012917/original  a978-3-11-074331-9  Duke University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  aEBA_DUK_ALL  aEBA_DUK_EALL  aEBA_DUK_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles